{"tid":353303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"橫頭磡邨36歲繼子斬傷37歲後父 警8小時後拉人","createTime":"2017-08-09T13:06:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T15:50:10.000Z","uid":17404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6f0c1532d8233334999a342b4fbb3151deccb70f","tid":353303,"uid":17404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T13:06:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170809&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57058576\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170809%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57058576&d=C4m1Kk2qynx16K1dV7oruDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=ee1af95c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170809%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57058576&h=254c4ed8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170809&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57058576</a><br />\n<br />\n黃大仙橫頭磡邨宏亮樓，一名姓潘37歲內地男子，與58歲本地妻子，以及妻子與前夫所生的36歲兒子，住在一個單位。凌晨2時許，潘熟睡中，繼子突然失常，持菜刀及生果刀向他襲擊，他兩邊肩膊及背部中刀受傷，負傷跑落地下大堂，向保安員求救。<br />\n<br />\n繼子傷人後棄刀逃去，救護員到場將傷者送院；警方持盾牌搜捕未有發現。現場消息指，繼子有精神病記錄，身高約1.7米、肥身材、蓄短黑髮，案發時身穿灰白色粗橫間條上衣，黑色短運動褲，螢光橙色褲腳及褲骨，黑色拖鞋。<br />\n<br />\n至早上約10時，警員在橫頭磡邨街頭拘捕該名36歲姓黃男子，他涉嫌傷人正被扣留調查，案件交由黃大仙警區重案組跟進。據悉，黃有精神病多年，今年初才由小欖精神病院出院。事發前並沒有與潘爭執。女戶主為夜班保安員，當時正上班，潘熟睡期間不料遇襲。街坊稱，女戶主早年帶同兒子「嫁到」此單位，與丈夫及家姑一家四口同住，惟兩三年前他們先後離世，剩下女戶主兩母子，直至去年才見到事件中的繼父出入。另外，疑犯過往有刑毀、車內盜竊、藏毒、藏有攻擊性武器等案底。有街坊稱，以往他亦不時滋擾街坊。"},{"pid":"cd1458ad821e12eab03df386b5e693b9ac9dcb9e","tid":353303,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T13:08:26.000Z","msg":"根本就係兩個中坑打交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01399776d7fe546b5dc3e2086de7470a97eea5a4","tid":353303,"uid":17081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T13:29:04.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://vignette4.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/f/f3/Mswow2.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20070116234418\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette4.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Ff%2Ff3%2FMswow2.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20070116234418&h=2a1fab3c&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"0ad2f0e02ef114b7eb49819675990478e4b54748","tid":353303,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T13:58:26.000Z","msg":"後生廿年支那佬 識嘆"},{"pid":"83a6fcff9c4e1e289f77b6d841806aa0144fb69d","tid":353303,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T14:13:12.000Z","msg":"勇武烈士怒斬支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa60588a81cc3fe12ec3ccf8cca0b36c96eaa762","tid":353303,"uid":4152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T14:16:59.000Z","msg":"37歲有個58歲老婆連36歲便宜仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98e049a69c9e4b47844b05682be093f3b0354a81","tid":353303,"uid":53238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T14:17:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>勇武烈士怒斬支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n勇條撚咩<br />\n斬人嗰個咪又係賤種<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>另外，疑犯過往有刑毀、車內盜竊、藏毒、藏有攻擊性武器等案底。有街坊稱，以往他亦不時滋擾街坊。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"224c34b72d1be99c6cf914ad0b668e5f6f347851","tid":353303,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T14:27:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>勇武烈士怒斬支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n勇條撚咩<br />\n斬人嗰個咪又係賤種<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>另外，疑犯過往有刑毀、車內盜竊、藏毒、藏有攻擊性武器等案底。有街坊稱，以往他亦不時滋擾街坊。</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n咪咁快拆穿好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc1c33a541808